{"surahDetails":{"id":86,"arabicName":"الطارق","banglaName":"রাতের আগন্তুক","englishName":"The Morning Star","enTranslatedName":"At-Tariq","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/86.mp3","totalAyah":17},"surah":{"id":86,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","bangl_text":"শপথ আকাশের এবং রাত্রিতে আগমনকারীর।","english_text":"By the sky and the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5932.mp3","colorText":"وَ[h:9999[ٱ][l[ل]سَّم[o[َا]ٓءِ وَ[h:14418[ٱ][l[ل]طَّارِ[q[ق]ِ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>سَّم<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓءِ وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>طَّارِ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>ِ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","bangl_text":"আপনি জানেন, যে রাত্রিতে আসে সেটা কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what is the night comer","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5933.mp3","colorText":"وَم[o[َآ] أَ[q:13858[دْ]رَ[n[ٮٰ]كَ مَا [h:14419[ٱ][l[ل]طَّارِ[q[ق]ُ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَم<span class=madda_obligatory>َآ</span> أَ<span class=qalaqah>دْ</span>رَ<span class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</span>كَ مَا <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>طَّارِ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>ُ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱلنَّجۡمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","bangl_text":"সেটা এক উজ্জ্বল নক্ষত্র।","english_text":"It is the piercing star","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5934.mp3","colorText":"ٱ[l[ل][g[نّ]َ[q:14420[جْ]مُ [h:14421[ٱ][l[ل]ثَّاقِ[q[ب]ُ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱ<span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span><span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َ<span class=qalaqah>جْ</span>مُ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>ثَّاقِ<span class=qalaqah>ب</span>ُ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"إِن كُلُّ نَفۡسٖ لَّمَّا عَلَيۡهَا حَافِظٞ","bangl_text":"প্রত্যেকের উপর একজন তত্ত্বাবধায়ক রয়েছে।","english_text":"There is no soul but that it has over it a protector","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5935.mp3","colorText":"إِ[f:8426[ن ك]ُلُّ نَفْ[u:14422[سٍ ل]َّ[g[مّ]َا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"إِ<span class=ikhafa>ن ك</span>ُلُّ نَفْ<span class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>سٍ ل</span>َّ<span class=ghunnah>مّ</span>َا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ","bangl_text":"অতএব, মানুষের দেখা উচিত কি বস্তু থেকে সে সৃজিত হয়েছে।","english_text":"So let man observe from what he was created","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5936.mp3","colorText":"فَلْيَ[f:14313[نظ]ُرِ [h:14314[ٱ]لْإِ[f:2732[نس]َ[n[ـٰ]نُ مِ[g[مّ]َ خُلِ[q[ق]َ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"فَلْيَ<span class=ikhafa>نظ</span>ُرِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْإِ<span class=ikhafa>نس</span>َ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>نُ مِ<span class=ghunnah>مّ</span>َ خُلِ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>َ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٖ دَافِقٖ","bangl_text":"সে সৃজিত হয়েছে সবেগে স্খলিত পানি থেকে।","english_text":"He was created from a fluid, ejected","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5937.mp3","colorText":"خُلِقَ م[a:840[ِن م]ّ[o[َا]ٓ[f:14423[ءٍ د]َافِ[q[ق]ٍ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"خُلِقَ م<span class=idgham_ghunnah>ِن م</span>ّ<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓ<span class=ikhafa>ءٍ د</span>َافِ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>ٍ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"يَخۡرُجُ مِنۢ بَيۡنِ ٱلصُّلۡبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","bangl_text":"এটা নির্গত হয় মেরুদন্ড ও বক্ষপাজরের মধ্য থেকে।","english_text":"Emerging from between the backbone and the ribs","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5938.mp3","colorText":"يَخْرُجُ م[i:4612[ِنۢ ب]َيْنِ [h:14424[ٱ][l[ل]صُّلْبِ وَ[h:14425[ٱ][l[ل]تَّر[o[َا]ٓئِ[q[ب]ِ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"يَخْرُجُ م<span class=iqlab>ِنۢ ب</span>َيْنِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>صُّلْبِ وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>تَّر<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓئِ<span class=qalaqah>ب</span>ِ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجۡعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় তিনি তাকে ফিরিয়ে নিতে সক্ষম।","english_text":"Indeed, Allah, to return him [to life], is Able","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5939.mp3","colorText":"إِ[g[نّ]َهُ[n[ۥ] عَلَىٰ رَ[q:14426[جْ]عِه[n[ِۦ] لَقَادِرٌ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"إِ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َهُ<span class=madda_normal>ۥ</span> عَلَىٰ رَ<span class=qalaqah>جْ</span>عِه<span class=madda_normal>ِۦ</span> لَقَادِرٌ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"يَوۡمَ تُبۡلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","bangl_text":"যেদিন গোপন বিষয়াদি পরীক্ষিত হবে","english_text":"The Day when secrets will be put on trial","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5940.mp3","colorText":"يَوْمَ تُ[q:14427[بْ]لَى [h:14428[ٱ][l[ل]سَّر[o[َا]ٓئِرُ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"يَوْمَ تُ<span class=qalaqah>بْ</span>لَى <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>سَّر<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓئِرُ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٖ وَلَا نَاصِرٖ","bangl_text":"সেদিন তার কোন শক্তি থাকবে না এবং সাহায্যকারীও থাকবে না।","english_text":"Then man will have no power or any helper","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5941.mp3","colorText":"فَمَا لَهُ[n[ۥ] مِ[f:5395[ن ق]ُوَّ[a:14429[ةٍ و]َلَا نَاصِرٍ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"فَمَا لَهُ<span class=madda_normal>ۥ</span> مِ<span class=ikhafa>ن ق</span>ُوَّ<span class=idgham_ghunnah>ةٍ و</span>َلَا نَاصِرٍ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجۡعِ","bangl_text":"শপথ চক্রশীল আকাশের","english_text":"By the sky which returns [rain]","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5942.mp3","colorText":"وَ[h:9999[ٱ][l[ل]سَّم[o[َا]ٓءِ ذَاتِ [h:14430[ٱ][l[ل]رَّ[q:14431[جْ]عِ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>سَّم<span class=madda_obligatory>َا</span>ٓءِ ذَاتِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>رَّ<span class=qalaqah>جْ</span>عِ <span class=end>١١</span>"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدۡعِ","bangl_text":"এবং বিদারনশীল পৃথিবীর","english_text":"And [by] the earth which cracks open","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5943.mp3","colorText":"وَ[h:9999[ٱ]لْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ [h:14432[ٱ][l[ل]صَّ[q:14433[دْ]عِ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>صَّ<span class=qalaqah>دْ</span>عِ <span class=end>١٢</span>"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلٞ فَصۡلٞ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কোরআন সত্য-মিথ্যার ফয়সালা।","english_text":"Indeed, the Qur'an is a decisive statement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5944.mp3","colorText":"إِ[g[نّ]َهُ[n[ۥ] لَقَوْ[f:14434[لٌ ف]َصْلٌ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"إِ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َهُ<span class=madda_normal>ۥ</span> لَقَوْ<span class=ikhafa>لٌ ف</span>َصْلٌ <span class=end>١٣</span>"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ","bangl_text":"এবং এটা উপহাস নয়।","english_text":"And it is not amusement","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5945.mp3","colorText":"وَمَا هُوَ بِ[h:14435[ٱ]لْهَزْلِ","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَمَا هُوَ بِ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْهَزْلِ <span class=end>١٤</span>"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَكِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"তারা ভীষণ চক্রান্ত করে","english_text":"Indeed, they are planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5946.mp3","colorText":"إِ[g[نّ]َهُمْ يَكِيدُونَ كَيْدًا","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"إِ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َهُمْ يَكِيدُونَ كَيْدًا <span class=end>١٥</span>"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيۡدٗا","bangl_text":"আর আমিও কৌশল করি।","english_text":"But I am planning a plan","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5947.mp3","colorText":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيْدًا","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيْدًا <span class=end>١٦</span>"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"فَمَهِّلِ ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ أَمۡهِلۡهُمۡ رُوَيۡدَۢا","bangl_text":"অতএব, কাফেরদেরকে অবকাশ দিন, তাদেরকে অবকাশ দিন, কিছু দিনের জন্যে।","english_text":"So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5948.mp3","colorText":"فَمَهِّلِ [h:14436[ٱ]لْكَ[n[ـٰ]فِرِينَ أَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدَۢا","juz":30,"ruku":528,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"فَمَهِّلِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْكَ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>فِرِينَ أَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدَۢا <span class=end>١٧</span>"}]}}